FX.name: DualComp
FX.description: This is a compressor which allows separate settings for the low frequency and high frequency range.

Parameters.name: FREQ
Parameters.explanation: Adjusts the crossover point between the high frequency and low frequency range.

Parameters.name: LoCMP
Parameters.explanation: Adjusts the compression depth in the low frequency range.

Parameters.name: HiCMP
Parameters.explanation: Adjusts the compression depth in the high frequency range.
